OL,3,CPETA praise Nottingham City council
OL,4,Cafter ban on non-vegan food in meetings
OL,6,FAnimal rights organisation PETA
OL,7,F(People for the Ethical Treatment of
OL,8,FAnimals) has praised Nottingham City
OL,9,FCouncil after it announced it will
OL,10,Fserve only plant-based food and drink
OL,11,Fat internal meetings.
OL,13,FThe change will come into play at the
OL,14,Fend of this month and was confirmed at
OL,15,Fa meeting last Monday 9 September,
OL,16,Ffollowing a question from a local
OL,17,Fresident.
