OL,3,CPETA praise Nottingham City council
OL,4,Cafter ban on non-vegan food in meetings
OL,6,FIn response to the city council's
OL,7,Fdecision decision, Dawn Carr, Peta's
OL,8,Fvice president of vegan corporate
OL,9,Fproject, said that: "Nottingham City
OL,10,FCouncil is fighting climate change
OL,11,Fwith diet change, and Peta is
OL,12,Fdelighted to see councillors taking
OL,13,Faction for animals while looking after
OL,14,Ftheir own health too.
OL,16,F"Peta applauds the authority for
OL,17,Fshining a green light on the benefits
OL,18,Fof eating vegan and hopes others will
OL,19,Ffollow its compassionate lead."
