OL,3,CPETA praise Nottingham City council
OL,4,Cafter ban on non-vegan food in meetings
OL,6,F"The decision followed lobbying from
OL,7,Fthe Plant-Based Councils campaign
OL,8,Fgroup, which described it as a
OL,9,F"logical and necessary step".
OL,11,FThe council's executive member for
OL,12,Fcarbon reduction, leisure and culture,
OL,13,FSam Lux, said at Monday's meeting that
OL,14,Fshe was "really happy" to confirm the
OL,15,Fmove after discussing it with council
OL,16,Fofficers.
