OL,3,CPETA praise Nottingham City council
OL,4,Cafter ban on non-vegan food in meetings
OL,6,FShe added there would also be a week
OL,7,Fof promotion of dairy alternatives for
OL,8,Fstaff to try plant-based milk in their
OL,9,Fdrinks from the coffee bar at the
OL,10,Fcouncil's Loxley House headquarters.
OL,12,FHowever, the National Farmers' Union
OL,13,F(NFU), which represents agricultural
OL,14,Fworkers across England and Wales,
OL,15,Fcriticised the policy change.
