OL,3,CPETA praise Nottingham City council
OL,4,Cafter ban on non-vegan food in meetings
OL,6,FNFU president Tom Bradshaw said: "What
OL,7,Fwe eat is a personal choice and not
OL,8,Fsomething which is imposed. Decisions
OL,9,Fshould be made in an informed way
OL,10,Ftaking into consideration the
OL,11,Fnutritional, environmental and
OL,12,Fbiodiversity benefits that eating a
OL,13,Fbalanced diet, including meat and
OL,14,Fdairy, provides.
OL,16,F"We engage regularly with local
OL,17,Fcouncils and others about the
OL,18,Fimportance of supporting local supply
OL,19,Fchains and the vital role farmers play
OL,20,Fat the heart of our rural communities.
